io consultants and head office heroes.<\/p>","colour_style":"dark","button_1_text":"Meet the Team","button_1_link":"https:\/\/www.nataliemariejewellery.com\/blogs\/news\/tagged\/these-hands","button_style":"underline"}},"aa07b19f-2029-4690-bcf3-58f3c299a0eb":{"type":"text-with-media","blocks":{"template--16096638042281__aa07b19f-2029-4690-bcf3-58f3c299a0eb-1678422871797a660f-0":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Screenshot_2023-02-22_at_5.27.12_pm.png"}}},"block_order":["template--16096638042281__aa07b19f-2029-4690-bcf3-58f3c299a0eb-1678422871797a660f-0"],"settings":{"remove_spacing_top":true,"remove_spacing_bottom":true,"enable_newsletter_subscribe":false,"klaviyo_form_id":"","media_position":"right","media_width":"7","content_position":"topLeftSticky","subheading":"","title":"<p>Our <em>Community<\/em><\/p>","description":"<p>Once we have sourced the perfect<br\/>stone and finalised the design, this is secured with a 50-75 per cent deposit. At this stage, we (Bespoke Customer Service) take over, and send over a deposit<br\/>invoice and document to sign which outlines our terms and conditions.<\/p>","colour_style":"dark","button_1_text":"","button_1_link":"","button_style":"underline"}},"375e1ab1-abf9-427c-a8ce-1aecefe0dfaf":{"type":"content-list","blocks":{"template--16176802988201__375e1ab1-abf9-427c-a8ce-1aecefe0dfaf-image-1":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/221207_NMJ_S53_2380-home-1200x1500_f2a145e5-acf2-41ac-8318-26dbaf6b2177.jpg","apply_overlay":false,"devices":"mobile_desktop","content_position":"underLeft","subheading":"","title":"","description":"","description_mobile":"","colour_style":"dark","button_1_text":"NMJ Essentials","button_1_link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/nmj-essentials","button_2_text":"","button_2_link":"","button_style":"underline"}},"template--16176802988201__375e1ab1-abf9-427c-a8ce-1aecefe0dfaf-image-2":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Sollune-Necklace-Go